tool_description: An API web scrapper that provides you with titles and links to front page video game news from around the web
name: Video Game News
title: Video Game News

api_list.name: all articles from all sources
api_list.description: Provides all articles from all sources
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://video-game-news.p.rapidapi.com/all"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "video-game-news.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
